 Hastashilpa Unnayan Utsav, an exhibition of crafts, artefacts and other products made by rural artisans of Bengal, at Swabhumi Sabhaghar, noon to 8 pm.

 Theatre

 Sutra, a dance-drama by Sharmila Biswas, at Bharatiyam, 6 pm.

 Three children?s plays, as part of Dwandwik Natyotsab, at Sarat Sadan, 5.30 pm.

